          </div>
          </p>
      </div>

      <div class='static-page__row'>
        <h3 class='static-page__subtitle static-page__subtitle--sinai'>Consulting Conservators</h3>
        <p class='static-page__text static-page__text--sinai'>
        Consulting conservators review and monitor the protocols and procedures that guide the selection, handling and tracking of manuscripts during the digitization process. They reviewed the two types of digitization system and the protocols for handling manuscripts on both, as well as compared the environmental conditions between the library and the digitization room to ensure that manuscripts can be safely transferred between the two locations. Consulting conservators also work with the Monastery Librarian to evaluate fragile codices prior to digitization.
        </p>
